1
00:00:00,840 --> 00:00:02,160
Previously on Babylon Berlin:

2
00:00:02,240 --> 00:00:05,120
I will guide you to the truth.

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:06,600
Gereon!

4
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:08,800
-Did you go to war?
-I followed my brother.

5
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:11,440
I came back alone.
My mother never got over that.

6
00:00:12,080 --> 00:00:13,800
For her, the wrong son came home.

7
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:16,880
Anno was officially declared dead.

8
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:19,520
-And now?
-We're here if you want us to.

9
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:21,680
Lotte? Where have you been?

10
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,880
Everywhere.

11
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:25,200
-I want to join homicide.
-No women there.

12
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:28,440
-I don't do detective sergeants.
-Don't worry.

13
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:30,280
Let's settle the matter between ourselves.

14
00:00:31,520 --> 00:00:33,040
What's the matter with you?

15
00:00:33,120 --> 00:00:35,840
Get lost!
I don't want to see you again.

16
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:42,080
-Mr. Benda is not a murderer.
-He's the boss of the polit police.

17
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:44,920
No! Fritz!

18
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:47,160
That Benda of yours, it was his people.

19
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:49,720
Tell me what to do and I'll do it.

20
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,160
Fritz, what are you doing here?

21
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,320
You're mistaking me.

22
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,080
What's this, Daddy?

23
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,520
Do you recognise me?

24
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,720
Anno?

25
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,400
Stop! What are you doing?

26
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,520
You can't go out there.

27
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:47,120
Don't go out there! Stay inside, mate!

28
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:58,320
We want our money back!

29
