FIVE WEEKS EARLIER
20 SEPTEMBER 1929

30
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:10,280
-Why so many rolls?
-I don't know.

31
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,760
-Morning.
-Didn't he...

32
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,920
-Morning. When did you get home?
-Morning.

33
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,840
Late. Didn't want to disturb you.

34
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,080
Don't get upset.

35
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:31,880
WOMEN'S PENAL INSTITUTION
BERLIN-FRIEDRICHSHAIN

36
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:46,120
REJECTED
REJECTED

37
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:51,360
You are very persistent in this matter.

38
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:54,200
It's my heartfelt wish, Madam.

39
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,320
Greta Overbeck and I are close.

40
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,840
She doesn't give us that impression.

41
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:02,920
-Why ever not?
-It doesn't say that here.

42
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,280
She expressedly refuses to see anybody.

43
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:08,680
In particular DS Charlotte Ritter.

44
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,800
I'm just an assistant detective.

45
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,440
It says DS here.

46
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,920
Well, I can't help you there.

47
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,960
You're not even related.

48
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,520
Please sign here.

49
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:42,480
One more thing, Weintraub.
This is Mr Ulrich from police records.

50
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,080
What does the joker want?

51
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,800
Dactyloscopy.

52
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,520
-Fingerprints.
-Just a formality.

53
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:51,920
-For the discharge?
-For our files. Prophylactical.

54
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,400
Precautionary.

55
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,480
Please.

56
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:09,480
Well then, show me how you do it.

57
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,120
Thumb.

58
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,840
This is part of it.

59
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,760
GATE 2

60
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,520
Look at that, Stick-it-in Fuchs.

61
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,760
Welcome.

62
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,560
Well, well, well.

63
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,960
Clothes become people, huh?

64
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,560
Senor Walter.

65
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,560
Cigarette?

66
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,840
Here you are.

67
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,800
Vera?

68
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,320
Mr. Weintraub.

69
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,800
Caught red-handed.

70
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,960
You know what? You go ahead.

71
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:46,440
-I'll go for a little spin with madam.
-They're all waiting.

72
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,720
All the more suspense.

73
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,280
Come closer.

74
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,920
Don't you worry.

75
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:05,280
I won't hurt you. Come on.

